            "The <em>rāspīg</em> (should recite) at the place of the <em>srōšāwarz: yaθā ahū vairiiō yō zaōtā frā.mē mrūtē</em> and the <em>zōt</em> should answer: <em>aθā ratuš</em>."</ab>
